claim.claim-text:
1. A wave planter device for drilling seeds comprised of
(a) a drawbar;
(b) a means to produce lateral movement of the draw bar comprised of at least one cylinder and a control system for the at least one cylinder;
(c) a means to moveably secure the means to produce lateral movement to a pulling vehicle comprised of a tractor;
(d) a moveable drawbar means for securing the at least one cylinder and the control system to the tractor;
(e) at least one row opener secured essentially perpendicular to the drawbar; and
(f) a means to connect the drawbar and the at least one row opener to the wave planter device
